high_descs: Turn around facing toaster on counter.
Walk over to toaster and take muffin from the counter.
Turn right, walk to microwave, turn left to face microwave.
Put muffin in microwave, cook the muffin, take the muffin out of microwave.
Turn left, walk to fridge, turn right facing fridge.
Put muffin on bottom shelf of fridge, close door.
anns.task_desc: Get the muffin, cook it in microwave, put muffin in fridge.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the stove
Pick up a brown egg from the counter
Move to the microwave to the end of the counter to the right
Heat the egg and close the door after getting the egg out of the microwave
Move to the fridge to the left of the stove
Place the egg inside and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a heated egg in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around head to the counter  near the toaster
Pick up the potato beside the toaster on the counter
Turn to your right and head to the microwave
Open the microwave place the potato in between the two eggs,  get the potato from the microwave
Turn to your left cross the room and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put the potato inside beside the mug
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato on the fridge
